TIDINGS OF JOY,
A New Singing Book for Sabbath Schools, etc., by D. E. Dortch.
The Music is New, Bright and Sparkling, carefully prepared and skilfully arranged, and is strictly
up to the times in every respect. By mail 25 cts. per copy, $3.00 per doz.; by express $2.40 per doz.
$20.00 per 100.
Address D. E. DORTCH, Columbia, Tenn.
PRECIOUS JEWELS,
FOR SABBATH SCHOOLS, BY J H. LESLIE & R. B. MAHAFFEY,
The Music is a skillful combination of SIMPLICITY, BEAUTY and E. CELLENCE. Strictly up with the
times in Words, Music, Quantity, Quality and Price. A Marvel of Elegance and Cheapness.
Sample copy 20 cts.; $1.80 per dozen in Board Covers; $15.00 per hundred.
The Musical Advocate,
A large four-page monthly, devoted exclusively to the interest of music in Public Schools, Sabbath

lion. Best of its class for the price in America. Only 50 cts. a year. Circulation over 6,000. Agents
wanted everywhere.

Price 30 cents.

Just Published, "EDEN OF THE BLEST."
